      "name": "Blackjack Cardgame Definition",
      "summary": "The Blackjack module defines a card-based game interface and logic for playing Blackjack within the app. It provides a highly interactive, visually rich user interface featuring animated cards, score displays, betting controls, and game outcome overlays. The core purpose is to facilitate a Blackjack game experience, including handling game states, managing player and dealer hands, calculating scores, implementing betting mechanics, and recording game results. It is designed for seamless integration into a larger card or casino-themed application, supporting both wide and compact display formats.",
